| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4763 — Recovery Inhibition (blackbasta)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2fd36345-986e-5c6c-88c0-5aa13d30cab1"
